OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FShoplifting hits record    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhigh in England and Wales  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Shoplifting offences recorded by police
OL,6, in England and Wales have risen to the 
OL,7, highest level in 20 years.             
OL,9,FMore than 430,000 offences were        
OL,10,Frecorded last year - up by more than a 
OL,11,Fthird than the previous 12 months to   
OL,12,FDecember 2022, according to the Office 
OL,13,Ffor National Statistics (ONS).         
OL,15,FThis is the highest figure since       
OL,16,Fcurrent police records began in 2003.  
OL,18,FOrganisations representing retailers   
OL,19,Fsay these figures represent a fraction 
OL,20,Fof the true number of incidents.       
